{"tid":2292819,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【暖心兄弟】9歲與7歲兒子入產房迎接B女　幫忙剪臍帶貼心照顧產後媽媽","createTime":"2020-11-19T20:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T04:07:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac8df2307a902cba4c5dddc4609d64e647a7e053","tid":2292819,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T20:37:34.000Z","msg":"媽媽生仔十級痛，在分娩的過程中，有丈夫會選擇陪產，給太太支持。美國一名媽媽育有兩兒，兒子知道媽媽懷有第3胎時，決定要陪產迎接妹妹。兩位哥哥雖然分別只有9歲及7歲，但做好準備，成為小小陪產員，並上了一堂震撼的生命教育課。<br />\n<br />\n9歲與7歲兒子陪產<br />\n綜合外媒報道，美國俄亥俄州有名媽媽Hollie Lau於去年5月16日誕下第3胎，當時產房有多名家人陪著她，包括9歲Charlie與7歲Hank兩兒子，他們一起迎接妹妹Robin。Robin健康地出世，重6磅8安士。<br />\n<br />\n回想Hollie懷上第3胎時，一家人都很開心，兩兒子更主動提出入產房陪伴媽媽，要第一時間見證妹妹的來臨。Hollie跟丈夫Bryan答應兒子的請求。<br />\n<br />\n可是，產婦分娩的過程未必人人都能承受，預計會見媽媽痛到大叫大嚷，胎兒血淋淋並連著臍帶出世等情景，對於2名不到10歲的男孩來說，是震撼的生命教育。故此，爸媽要兒子先參加產前班，讓Charlie和Hank看了不少嬰兒生世的影片，要他們知道分娩正常程序和做好心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n兒子為B女剪臍帶<br />\n去年5月中，Hollie如期做產前檢查，怎料發現胎兒心跳減慢，立即到醫院作緊急分娩，直到凌晨時，Hollie出現宮縮作動，馬上要長輩叫Charlie和Hank起床來醫院。Hollie母親表示是有史以來最快叫到這兩名孩子起床，他們很興奮期待，馬上準備好，希望盡快到媽媽身邊。<br />\n<br />\n兩兄弟貼心地化身照顧者，在媽媽身旁鼓勵她。爸媽當時有擔心兒子或會覺得分娩過程血腥，擔憂他們會恐懼不安。可是兩兒子選擇全程待著，握著媽媽手。大兒子Charlie更為BB女剪臍帶，雖然他展露出惶恐的神情，但最終成功剪臍帶。產後，兒子們留在病房照顧媽媽，幫她蓋被子、梳頭髮、攬抱媽媽等。媽媽感受至深︰<br />\n&quot;兒子握住我的手，幫助丈夫向我的背部施壓助產，參與了我最艱苦的生仔過程，給了我力量。兒子看到生育過程，感到生命的可貴！&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2805000/2807321/BB_thumb_20201119_E_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2805000%2F2807321%2FBB_thumb_20201119_E_1024.jpg&h=7e205ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2805000/2807321/06_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2805000%2F2807321%2F06_1024.jpg&h=4482dd4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2805000/2807321/05_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2805000%2F2807321%2F05_1024.jpg&h=f948b184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2805000/2807321/03_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2805000%2F2807321%2F03_1024.jpg&h=59ad6e59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2805000/2807321/p04_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2805000%2F2807321%2Fp04_1024.jpg&h=0818df3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f411726f4fd7ef1e71d923e2fbdf3dcbc5dd8aeb","tid":2292819,"uid":43373,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T20:42:35.000Z","msg":"以為七歲搞大咗個九歲既肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1cf4a30c617d70bc880cae52b9d33037725d272","tid":2292819,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T23:15:19.000Z","msg":"其實都好"},{"pid":"863422943626fc2ec2f69ab24ce192c8c4d95ed8","tid":2292819,"uid":71511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T00:05:23.000Z","msg":"so sweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d19e2306c6b916aa8bc43dc317c4fd19ea81d6","tid":2292819,"uid":161174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T00:06:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"feec8ca17a753c610da114de344d253daa1cc440","tid":2292819,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T00:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c850e83d9b3a48f5039ab51baa2b4ce80e7cf1a","tid":2292819,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T00:17:10.000Z","msg":"<i